description: This common Cooter purrs with a rating of 4, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 4, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, Box for East, Box for South, and 1 for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [4 Votes, Common]
